April 11 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Friday. To inform us of other job changes, email moves@thomsonreuters.com.

DEUTSCHE BANK AG <DBKGn.DE> The bank has hired senior Credit Suisse Group AG <CSGN.VX> investment banker, Rahul Chawla, to head its structured finance business in India, two sources with direct knowledge of the development said.